Complete UI redesign of sport-workout.tsx and sport-program-view.tsx

Applied dark hi-tech theme with glassmorphism and emerald accents across all
workout phases (select, warmup, active, completing, done) and all workout modes
(sets, timer, overview, pose_timer, overviewEntry).

Key visual changes:
- Gradient hero header on select screen (emerald-teal-cyan)
- Glassmorphism cards (bg-card/50, backdrop-blur-sm, border-border/50)
- Emerald gradient CTAs with shadow glow effects
- Dark-themed modals with backdrop blur
- Consistent label styling (10px uppercase tracking-wider)
- Dark-themed input fields (bg-secondary/50 border-border/50)
- Emerald accent colors for timers, counters, and badges
- Updated stat cards on completing/done screens with colored icons
- AI analysis cards with themed borders (emerald/amber/purple)
- sport-program-view.tsx fully rewritten with matching design tokens
- Removed all legacy light-mode-only styles (bg-emerald-100, bg-muted, etc.)
